<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Reverify Email for â€“ {{userName}}</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #f4f6f8;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #333333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 550px;
      margin: 50px auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 40px 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    }
    .logo {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }
    .logo img {
      width: 80px;
      height: auto;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      color: #0d6efd;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #555555;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .button-wrapper {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 35px 0;
    }
    .verify-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      background-color: #0d6efd;
      color: #ffffff !important;
      border-radius: 50px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .verify-btn:hover {
      background-color: #084298;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999999;
      margin-top: 40px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #0d6efd;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .footer a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">
      <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/1200x/e9/b2/67/e9b2670484d31f700283b522c8237e56.jpg" alt="Company Logo" />
    </div>
    <h1>Reverify Email for {{userName}}</h1>
    <p>
      Hi <strong>{{userName}}</strong>,
    </p>
    <p>
      Thank you for creating an account with us. To complete your registration and activate your account, please verify your email by clicking the button below.
    </p>
    <div class="button-wrapper">
      <a class="verify-btn" href="http://localhost:8002/user/verify/{{token}}">
        Verify My Email
      </a>
    </div>
    <p>
      For security reasons, this verification link will expire in 15 minutes.<br/>
      If you did not initiate this request, you may safely ignore this email.
    </p>
    
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; 2025 Priyajit Debnath. All rights reserved.<br />
      Need help? Contact our
      <a href="https://www.facebook.com/iampd10official/">support team</a>.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
